    <item>
      <title>Bannon Tantrum</title>
      <link>https://sidecar.keithjgrant.com/drinks/french-kiss/</link>
      <pubDate>Mon, 08 Jan 2018 12:21:43 -0500</pubDate>
      
      <guid>https://sidecar.keithjgrant.com/drinks/french-kiss/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;As always, use only &lt;a href=&#34;https://sidecar.keithjgrant.com/ingredients/vermouth&#34;&gt;high quality vermouth&lt;/a&gt; that is fresh (less than three months old).&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;2 oz sweet vermouth&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;2 oz dry vermouth&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Build in a rocks glass. Add a lemon twist.&lt;/p&gt;
</description>
